{"comments":"SignedData — Pure data structure for signed payloads.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nSignedData is a molecule that wraps any serializable content with:\n- Content hash (SHA-256 of the payload)\n- Signer identifier (who signed)\n- Signature bytes (the cryptographic signature)\n- Timestamp (when it was signed)\n\nThis module does NOT perform actual cryptographic signing — that happens\nat the runtime boundary. This module defines the pure data structure\nthat represents signed data.\n\n## Why SignedData?\n\nAt billion-agent scale, agents need:\n- Verifiable authorship of data\n- Non-repudiation (signer can't deny signing)\n- Foundation for x402 payments and EIP-712 signatures\n- Pure representation without FFI\n\n## Signature Schemes (represented, not implemented)\n\nThe signature bytes can represent:\n- ECDSA (secp256k1 for Ethereum, secp256r1 for WebAuthn)\n- EdDSA (Ed25519)\n- RSA-PSS\n- HMAC (symmetric, for trusted contexts)\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Attestation.SHA256 (content hashing)\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Attestation.Timestamp\n\n## Dependents\n\n- x402 payment flows\n- EIP-712 typed data signing\n- Document attestation\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Signed data molecule.\n\nWraps content with cryptographic signature metadata.\nThe actual signature verification happens at runtime.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["contentHash",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","SHA256"],"SHA256Hash"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["signer",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","SignedData"],"SignerId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["signature",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["timestamp",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Timestamp"],"Timestamp"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["scheme",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","SignedData"],"SignatureScheme"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[179,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/SignedData.purs","start":[173,1]},"title":"SignedData"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[112,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/SignedData.purs","start":[112,3]},"title":"ECDSA_secp256k1"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[113,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/SignedData.purs","start":[113,3]},"title":"ECDSA_secp256r1"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/SignedData.purs","start":[114,3]},"title":"Ed25519"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[115,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/SignedData.purs","start":[115,3]},"title":"RSA_PSS"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[116,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/SignedData.purs","start":[116,3]},"title":"HMAC_SHA256"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[117,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/SignedData.purs","start":[117,3]},"title":"Unknown"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation"